&lt;p&gt;Each resource can have a machine readable description in JSON-LD format&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section typeof='http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Slide'&gt;
&lt;img src='https://ptsefton.com/2021/06/11/or-2021-ro-crate/Slide4.png' alt='📂
