&lt;p&gt;There are now enough things happening with RO-Crate that it is getting hard to keep track of it all  - this slide is an incomplete view of what’s happening now.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section typeof='http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Slide'&gt;
&lt;img src='https://ptsefton.com/2021/06/11/or-2021-ro-crate/Slide17.png' alt='
